     CL2                   END
     CL3         FJRYO     ADD  ZJRYO     FJRYO   90
     CL3         FSRYO     ADD  ZSRYO     FSRYO  110
     CL3         FQKIN     ADD  ZQKIN     FQKIN  112
     CL3         FNKIN     ADD  ZNKIN     FNKIN  112
     CL3         FSKIN     ADD  ZSKIN     FSKIN  102
     CL3                   WRITEGBFPR834
     CL3         L         ADD  1         L
     CL3                   Z-ADD0         ZJRYO
     CL3                   Z-ADD0         ZSRYO
